Ubuntu Virtual Machine

Followed instructions here for build env: https://github.com/esp8266/esp8266-wiki/wiki/Toolchain

Makefile mod to: ESPTOOL = /opt/Espressif/esptool-py/esptool.py

ESP
TX		GND
CH_PD	GPIO2				ANTENA
RST		GPIO0
VCC		RX				

Flash:
ESP			TTL
VCC			VCC (3.3V)
GND			GND
TX			RX
RX			TX
RST			VCC	(3.3V)
CH_PD		RTS
GPIO0		DTR

Run:
GPIO0		DISCONNECTED
CH_PD		VCC (3.3V)




